# UI page patterns (livotale-ui)

Follow `specs/platform/ui-page-patterns.md`.

## List pages (`ListPageShell`)

- `PageHeader`: title left, **primary action** right (e.g. Add lead, Add package)
- `ListToolbar`: search + Apply/Reset + filter fields in grid
- `DataTable`: row click → detail route
- `PaginationControls`: below table

## Detail pages

- **Back arrow** (`FiArrowLeft`) icon button **left of title** — use `DetailPageShell` or `EntityDetailShell`
- Title = entity name; description = secondary id/meta
- Header **actions** (delete, preview) align right in `PageHeader`
- View/Edit tabs: `EntityDetailShell` + `?tab=view|edit`
- **All tabs**: sync URL via `useUrlTabState` (`?tab=`, `?section=`, `?profileSection=`, `?mode=` on public routes)
- **Log-style fields** (remarks, notes, call logs): `LogTextarea` + limits from `@/utils/fieldLimits`

## Primary vs secondary fields

CRM/enquiry forms: **name + phone required**; email, city, package, message optional (collapsed).

## Routes

```
/admin/{entity}           → list
/admin/{entity}/new       → create (`:id` = `new`)
/admin/{entity}/:id       → detail
```

Reference: `AdminEnquiriesPage`, `AdminPackagesPage`, `PatientsPage`, `PatientDetailPage`.
